commit.message:
dwarf2asm.c (eh_data_format_name): Add names for "pointer size" variants of non-absolute encodings.

        * dwarf2asm.c (eh_data_format_name): Add names for "pointer size"
        variants of non-absolute encodings.

From-SVN: r42178
